Description:
Gorgeous home in a great location !
Appointments by private inspections only !
10 Sheaf Road, Truganina
Wonderfully presented and dressed with class throughout is this gorgeous contemporary showstopper just perfect for those who won't compromise on quality.
This young family home is situated in one of the best and upcoming estates of Truganina The "Elements Estate". The property is in close proximity to the proposed school and the shopping centre and a stones throw to the future Truganina train station which offer buyers an ease of convenience.
10 Sheaf Road, Truganina is a fabulous single storey house with intelligent zoning, which sees a spacious floor plan layout playing host to an open-plan living, dining arrangement & home to a nice kitchen with 20 mm stone benchtop that delights with 900 mm gas cook top & great sized pantry.
The home consists of three bedrooms with the very spacious master bedroom offering a walk in robe and an en-suite . The remaining two bedrooms come with built in robes and are serviced by a central bathroom.
Inspired features are everywhere:
- High Ceilings, downlights & window Blinds and security doors
- All upgraded doors, flat roof tiles and an upgraded porch.
- Spacious pantry , 20 mm stone benchtop, 900 mm gas cook top & dishwasher
- Beautiful tiled splashback wall to wall & overhead cupboards
- Laminate timber flooring in all living areas and carpets in the bedrooms.
- Ducted Heating & Cooling - Making you feel comfortable all around the year
- Fully landscaped low maintenance front and backyard with artificial turf & concreting around the house
- Great sized timbre deck in the backyard to entertain as many friends in the weekend.
- Double garage and many more.
Ray White welcomes you and looks forward to meeting you at the private inspection as this will not stay long !!
Call Gary on 0410 947 568 today to set an appointment for private inspection!!
(PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTION)

Description:
Location! Location !! Location!!!
Ray White Truganina is proud to present this beautiful low maintenance three bedrooms, two-bathrooms home located in a prime location, move-in ready and filled with great opportunities! Equipped with a generous sized back yard and a low maintenance front yard, it is perfect for any family wanting that house that can cater to their needs of a hassle-free home or an ideal investment to build your portfolio.
They say you cant change the location , and this is a perfect example .This property is walking distance to St Clares Catholic Primary School, Yara Child Care Centre and in close proximity to Truganina P9 school, Westbourne Grammar School, , Al-Taqwa College, Williams Landing Railway Station, Tarneit Railway Station and Wyndham Village Shopping Centre.
FEATURES:
· Master bedroom with Ensuite and BIR
· Spacious kitchen with modern appliances and dishwasher
· Low Maintenance Yards
. Seperate Outdoor entertainment area
· Evaporative Cooling
· Ducted Heating
· Downlights
· Spacious laundry room with storage
It also offers you great natural lighting with the large windows and sliding glass door to the backyard!
This beautiful home could be yours. INSPECT before its GONE!! Contact Kartik on 0466 892 975 or Mark on 0425 400 600 to discuss further. Photo ID is a must for all inspections. Description:
Exceptional Value - Great Family Comfort !!
This beautifully presented home set on a quiet street, standing tall on 535m2(approx) embraces family living and is wonderfully easy to maintain. Boasting a flowing floorplan, this home delivers ease and comfort, while providing spacious living for a growing family.
• 3 oversize bedrooms with build-in-robes
• Central bathroom with separate toilet
• Separate Laundry
• Large Garage/Workshop (6m x 4.9m)
Entertaining is a breeze and dinners are certainly not limited to the dining area. Your private pergola is the perfect setting for those BBQ sessions and alfresco dinners. Further along, a large landscaped backyard provides the perfect backdrop for outdoor play space for children to run around and indulge in some backyard fun.
Other notable highlights include gas wall heater, split system cooling, separate laundry room, window fittings and so much more
Additionally, indulge in lifestyle conveniences with a short stroll to shops, restaurants and medical centre. Walking distance to local schools, bus-stop, parklands and walking trails along the Werribee River. Moments from Werribee township and M1 freeway access. This home certainly offers location, lifestyle and the opportunity to enter the Werribee property market.
Please contact Eyad Khudruj on 0414 711 647 or Ibrahim Khudruj on 0450 607 741 for further particulars.
Photo ID required for all inspections.

Description:
Effortlessly Enticing Family Home
LJ Hooker Point Cook presents 32 Teatree Terrace, Point Cook. Easy and effortless, this contemporary family home offers superb living across a sprawling single-storey. Set on a desirable 612m2 (approx) block, this residence offers premium comfortability with three bedrooms plus study/fourth bedroom, two bathrooms and three living zones. Nestled within the Lincoln Heath Estate, this pristine home enjoys a splendid location, surrounded by serene parklands and convenient amenities.
- Quality built by Burbank Homes, the property begins with a welcoming entrance hall, where natural light, neutral tones and gleaming white tiles offer an enticing glimpse of what is to come.
- Framed by glass and with a beautiful outlook, the first of three living zones is the formal lounge and dining room, a versatile space increasing the functionality of this family home. The family and meals area is bright and spacious and is overseen by the kitchen, an expansive entertaining zone which seamlessly transitions to the outdoor deck. Finally, a private and peaceful family retreat/rumpus room is tucked away at the rear of the home.
- A chefs haven, the gourmet kitchen offers state-of-the-art appliances including a 900mm stainless-steel upright gas cooker, rangehood and dishwasher. There is also plenty of storage and bench space including breakfast bar with shelving and pantry.
- Located at the front of the home, the master suite is a decadent retreat and remarkably spacious, including a walk-in-robe and en suite. Two further bedrooms offer built-in robes and share access to the central bathroom while the study can easily be utilized as a home office or fourth bedroom.
- Further highlights of this exceptional home include a double remote-control garage with both internal and drive-through access, separate laundry, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, split system air-conditioning and low maintenance landscaped gardens including artificial turf in the backyard.
Lincoln Heath Estate offers residents amenities including wetlands, parks, playgrounds and barbeque areas. Conveniently positioned near several schools including coveted Alamanda College and Featherbrook College and recreational precincts including Point Cook Reserve and Point Cook Coastal Park, Sanctuary Lakes Shopping Centre and Point Cook Town Centre. Public transportation options include regular bus routes and nearby Williams Landing train station.
Note. All stated dimensions are approximate only. Particulars given are for general information only and do not constitute any representation on the part of the vendor or agent.

Description:
Perfect block of land in the Albright Estate - Truganina
The Phone Code for this property is: 57265. Please quote this number when phoning or texting.
This large 624 m2 block of land (16 metres wide frontage and 39 metres depth) provides an opportunity to build your dream home on a perfectly shaped lot. Located in Albright Estate, Truganina, this block lies within an area which offers various amenities within the new community. Being 22 kilometres from the Melbourne CBD, the area provides direct access to the West Gate Freeway, reaching the city in 35 minutes by car. The city can be alternatively reached with an easy train ride taken from Tarneit station; or better yet, from the future Truganina train station to be built near the estate.
This property is advantageously located close by to a future government primary school, sports fields, and community and early learning centres. Additionally, established shopping centres and libraries in Tarneit and Williams Landing are only a few minutes drive away, with a future Truganina town centre to also be built nearby.
Don't miss this rare opportunity to buy one of the few remaining big blocks in this rapidly-growing, highly-sought area in Truganina. This land is already titled and ready to be built on.

Description:
East Facing & Easement free Ready to Build Titled Block in Elpis Estate
Rajesh & Ray White Tarneit Proudly presents you this great opportunity to build your dream home, on this beautiful titled block of land in the highly sought after Elpis estate in Truganina. Elpis is one of the most exciting new developments in the west.
While born of big thinking, Elpis is being developed with absolute attention to detail. It has taken literally years of effort and a team with great vision to create an estate that offers residents the best of the present, while recognising the heritage of the past.
Within close distance to Tarneit train stations and nearby bus lines is designed to give the entire family easy access to the things that matter, starting with the essentials like Schools, Parks, Transport System and Supermarkets. And if you need to get into the city, Williams Landing or Tarneit train stations and easy access to the Princes Freeway will make it even quick and easy.
21 km to CBD through M1 freeway. This lot is in close proximity to established popular schools such as Truganina P9 school, Westbourne Grammar School, Al-Taqwa College, Williams Landing, Tarneit Train Stations, proposed Truganina Train Station, Parks, Walking Tracks, Local Community Centre, Shops, this wont last long!
It is an address perfectly positioned for convenience and growth. A place where you will take pride in your community and where your neighbours will become your friends.
An opportunity like this is rare to come by and will not last long! To be a part of this exciting experience, living a balanced and active lifestyle at Elpis estaste, please call Rajesh on 0433 240 392 to find out more!
